{"type": "article", "id": 42655, "title": "「这世界」他一天之内在海滩上捡了 35 大袋垃圾，然后把它们变成了艺术品", "description": "然后他办了个展览，叫“塑料时代”", "date": "2017-07-04T05:39:25Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 7, "name": "艺术"}, {"id": 812, "name": "环境"}, {"id": 1543, "name": "这世界"}, {"id": 7781, "name": "垃圾"}], "category": 5, "column": 13, "author": 4695, "comment_count": 10, "praise_count": 63, "image": "img/article/article_show/20170704132352XjbEyFmpvz3ahkO7.jpg", "contents": "<p nocleanhtml=\"true\">夏天到了呢。一到夏天，总想去海边。但现在，要找一片环境好的海滩还真是困难。今天的故事，就和海滩有关。</p><p>罗伯·阿诺德是 Rame 半岛海滩护理团队的成员。他经常在 Tregantle 海滩上散步，但今年 4 月的一天，海滩的景象令他震惊了——平时平静的海滩密密麻麻地被大量小塑料物品覆盖。就好像沙滩被覆盖上了一层塑料毯子。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707041311463bw4HK57z1SjQqnD.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>“我习惯了在海边清理垃圾，因为四年来我一直都在这样做，但这次真的让我很震惊很绝望。我觉得这是在太过分了，根本来不及清理，但我觉得我们还是可以试试。这件事大概就像是把这些东西都吐给了我们，我们应该是有责任把它们清理赶紧的。”</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131254s3ZIeSWlBGhwnpx2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>接着，罗伯就开始拿着垃圾袋清理了起来。在当地志愿者的帮助下，他一共清理出了 35 大袋垃圾。清理的时候，他还仔细看了下垃圾的成分，发现里头有塑料玩具兵营，有乐高潜水艇、坦克玩具、脚蹼以及各种各样的小玩意儿，其中大部分都是塑料做的。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131328jcu4KTwYDWhP9foZ.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131645W8E0BkCIHXVvh1Yt.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332857\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131648iDsrHbZWeVuz0jBP.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\" class=\"\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"\"><div><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\"><br></span></div><p><span style=\"color: rgb(54, 54, 54); font-size: 18px; text-align: justify;\">摆在一起，意外地还有一种艺术感。</span></p></figcaption></figure></div><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131341mV1PCZEtOQcDvI7d.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>如果认真地分门别类，再整齐地排列一下，还意外地有种静物摆拍的效果。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131411Cv5bOaqo2ZjD3Kfg.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>哦对了，忘了说了，罗伯还是当地的艺术家。这些塑料玩具在他的巧手之下简直像获得了新生。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131447etWBQ6jNw4siFm9u.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.735714\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>面对这些辛辛苦苦地收拾完的垃圾，罗伯觉得不能就简简单单地把它们扔了。为了让大家更明白现在海洋遇到了这样的问题，他把这些垃圾按照上面那样的归纳排列法变成了一种艺术品，然后送去了当地的 Liskeard 博物馆展出。这个展览的名字就叫“塑料时代”。“塑料时代”，这真是对我们这个年代最好的命名。</p><div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131616zyuZGY3qJsKnTgSB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131616kZcbm24qNHpfz0Ki.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131616f0Z9vR2OCrJYFU7n.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131617ILJKeB2EqS0cN1oG.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131617d3ihysnvrMZw6OAo.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131618aSiMxl9kmBCwGpHd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201707041316180yQS9Bjun6EcWIlH.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131618y9X1tzmfuCZH6aMb.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131619QkJ8fmXPtylzLYu0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131619nLgG741fSQx0NjdI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.750000\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131619zQtMDudl78nwc4NC.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"1.332857\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20170704131620Z15WogVHTpqa3v6D.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.838571\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div><p>看到这里，大家也来回忆一下吧，当年我们那些经常把玩的塑料小玩意最后都去哪儿了？</p><p class=\"\"><br></p><p class=\"\">题图来自&nbsp;<a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow\" jsaction=\"mousedown:irc.rl;keydown:irc.rlk\" data-noload=\"\" tabindex=\"0\" href=\"https://www.google.com/url?sa=i&amp;rct=j&amp;q=&amp;esrc=s&amp;source=images&amp;cd=&amp;cad=rja&amp;uact=8&amp;ved=0ahUKEwjM66Ly8O7UAhUEMj4KHQsQC0IQjB0IBg&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fcommons.wikimedia.org%2Fwiki%2FFile%3ABeach_strewn_with_plastic_debris_(8080500982).jpg&amp;psig=AFQjCNGg4md-TI7SS2vvivwM1IgZS2QJDQ&amp;ust=1499232086931569\" data-ved=\"0ahUKEwjM66Ly8O7UAhUEMj4KHQsQC0IQjB0IBg\" data-href=\"https://commons.wikimedia.org/wiki/File:Beach_strewn_with_plastic_debris_(8080500982).jpg\">Wikimedia Commons</a></p>"}